org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM work_packages WHERE work_packages.project_id IN (SELECT DISTINCT projects.id FROM projects INNER JOIN enabled_modules ON projects.id = enabled_modules.project_id AND enabled_modules.name IN ('work_package_tracking') AND projects.active = True WHERE projects.active = True) AND work_packages.id = "$1" LIMIT 1
